id isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/leading-israeli-protest-group-files-defamation-suits-against-right-wing-slander/0000018f-ed82-d36e-abcf-fdc6e8f60000</guid></item><item><title>TikTok 令以色列担忧。与此同时，22 名部长迷上了这款应用</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/tech-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-worried-about-tiktok-meanwhile-22-of-its-ministers-are-hooked-on-the-app/0000018f-ed72-d9ce-a5cf-ffffd4610000</link><description>“TikTok 对国家安全构成战略威胁”：以色列议会的一次讨论暴露了以色列政府未能解决日益严重的操纵社交平台问题，该平台被 380 万以色列人使用，其中包括国家安全部长</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 13:42:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/tech-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-worried-about-tiktok-meanwhile-22-of-its-ministers-are-hooked-on-the-app/0000018f-ed72-d9ce-a5cf-ffffd4610000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对加沙近东救济工程处学校的袭击造成数十人死亡；以色列国防军：哈马斯利用建筑物作为基地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/dozens-killed-in-israeli-strike-on-unrwa-school-in-gaza-idf-hamas-used-building-as-base/0000018f-ed20-dba5-afdf-ffb2a6480000</link><description>虽然以色列军方表示，近东救济工程处在努塞拉特的学校关押着参加 10 月 7 日的哈马斯和伊斯兰圣战恐怖分子精英，但哈马斯表示，该学校关押着流离失所的加沙人，并不是军事大院。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 11:32:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/dozens-killed-in-israeli-strike-on-unrwa-school-in-gaza-idf-hamas-used-building-as-base/0000018f-ed20-dba5-afdf-ffb2a6480000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院前院长因个人原因辞去国际法院职务</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/former-israeli-supreme-court-president-resigns-from-icj-citing-personal-reasons/0000018f-ecad-dba5-afdf-febfb2e80000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡总理现在必须任命大屠杀幸存者阿哈龙·巴拉克的继任者，巴拉克认为，只要以色列履行《种族灭绝公约》规定的义务，以色列就没有义务停止加沙南部的战斗</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 10:48:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/former-israeli-supreme-court-president-resigns-from-icj-citing-personal-reasons/0000018f-ecad-dba5-afdf-febfb2e80000</guid></item><item><title>当以色列人发现自己被困在贝鲁特机场时</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-06-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-israelis-find-themselves-stranded-at-beiruts-airport/0000018f-e7b6-d11f-a5cf-e7bfac3b0000</link><description>以色列军队一直在干扰 GPS 服务，以迷惑敌人。重新找回失去的方向感的机会</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 10:32:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-06-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-israelis-find-themselves-stranded-at-beiruts-airport/0000018f-e7b6-d11f-a5cf-e7bfac3b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在黎巴嫩边境附近真主党无人机袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-hezbollah-drone-attack-near-lebanon-border/0000018f-ecef-dcb4-a38f-fdefb19d0000</link><description>参谋军士。 (res.) 拉斐尔·考德斯 (Refael Kauders) 在真主党无人机袭击以色列北部边境德鲁兹城镇胡尔菲什 (Hurfeish) 附近的军事阵地时身亡</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 10:07:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-hezbollah-drone-attack-near-lebanon-border/0000018f-ecef-dcb4-a38f-fdefb19d0000</guid></item><item><title>恐怖分子计划袭击以色列领土开火，突破加沙缓冲区，以色列国防军士兵被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/terrorists-planning-raid-on-israeli-soil-breach-buffer-zone-with-gaza-fire-at-idf-forces/0000018f-ec7f-dcb4-a38f-fd7f40ad0000</link><description>至少三名恐怖分子闯入以色列控制的加沙边境缓冲区，其装备表明他们计划袭击以色列军事基地或边境社区，被以色列军队击毙</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 08:45:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/terrorists-planning-raid-on-israeli-soil-breach-buffer-zone-with-gaza-fire-at-idf-forces/0000018f-ec7f-dcb4-a38f-fd7f40ad0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯声称以色列和美国停火提议存在差异，要求调解员澄清</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/hamas-claims-disparity-between-israeli-and-u-s-cease-fire-deals-requests-clarification/0000018f-ec5c-da58-a1ef-fcde15270000</link><description>哈马斯在发给巴勒斯坦各派别的一份备忘录中表示，在与调解人会谈后，很明显以色列只对实施该提案的第一阶段感兴趣，并且避免承诺从加沙完全撤军</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 07:46:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/hamas-claims-disparity-between-israeli-and-u-s-cease-fire-deals-requests-clarification/0000018f-ec5c-da58-a1ef-fcde15270000</guid></item><item><title>过去 16 年里我看过每一次耶路撒冷旗帜游行。这是最丑的一个</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/if-jerusalem-day-is-an-accurate-thermometer-of-israeli-society-the-diagnosis-is-terminal/0000018f-eab4-d463-a19f-ffbd44ad0000</link><description>前几年，官员们做出了一些努力来平息事态。今年，年轻人似乎可以随意呼喊种族主义口号、骚乱以及攻击他们遇到的任何人。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 03:09:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/if-jerusalem-day-is-an-accurate-thermometer-of-israeli-society-the-diagnosis-is-terminal/0000018f-eab4-d463-a19f-ffbd44ad0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和真主党之间的边缘政策可能将双方推向边缘</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/brinkmanship-between-israel-and-hezbollah-could-push-both-sides-over-the-edge/0000018f-e9f1-dc46-a5bf-f9f58e310000</link><description>以色列总参谋部努力向真主党展示全面战争将带来的代价。对黎巴嫩的破坏将是巨大的，但对以色列北部和中部城市可能造成的破坏与哈马斯所经历的任何破坏都不一样</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 03:00:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/brinkmanship-between-israel-and-hezbollah-could-push-both-sides-over-the-edge/0000018f-e9f1-dc46-a5bf-f9f58e310000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人报告以色列军队与武装分子交火后在约旦河西岸杰宁造成三人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article-live/israel-terrorists-who-took-part-in-october-7-massacre-killed-in-strike-on-hamas-compound/0000018f-eb4c-d4cf-abcf-ef4d922b0000</link><description>以色列国防军宣布一名在加沙战斗中丧生的士兵死亡 ■ 加沙官员称，以色列袭击努塞拉特学校造成 40 人死亡 ■ 由于财务状况，巴勒斯坦权力机构将向其员工支付一半工资 ■ 以色列国防军宣布一名在黎巴嫩边境附近的无人机袭击中受伤的士兵死亡 ■ 三人恐怖分子在试图从加沙南部进入以色列时被杀</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 02:18:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article-live/israel-terrorists-who-took-part-in-october-7-massacre-killed-in-strike-on-hamas-compound/0000018f-eb4c-d4cf-abcf-ef4d922b0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡像夜里的小偷一样潜入什莫纳城。但他害怕的是市长，而不是真主党</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-snuck-into-kiryat-shmona-but-its-the-mayor-he-fears-not-hezbollah/0000018f-ea61-d4cf-abcf-ee61348b0000</link><description>一位小政客，令我们感到羞耻的是，他被称为“总理”，他拒绝会见这座陷入困境的北方城市的市长。内塔尼亚胡的战争时间表是为了满足他的政治需要而量身定制的，他的政府从未显得如此脱节和迟钝</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 22:13:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-snuck-into-kiryat-shmona-but-its-the-mayor-he-fears-not-hezbollah/0000018f-ea61-d4cf-abcf-ee61348b0000</guid></item><item><title>真主党无人机袭击以色列北部，造成十二人受伤，其中一人伤势严重</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/twelve-wounded-one-critically-by-hezbollah-drone-strike-in-northern-israel/0000018f-e9d8-da58-a1ef-f9dacca50000</link><description>以色列国防军正在调查为什么袭击前没有响起警报。真主党声称对此负责，称这是对以色列前一天在黎巴嫩南部发动袭击的回应</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 19:47:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/twelve-wounded-one-critically-by-hezbollah-drone-strike-in-northern-israel/0000018f-e9d8-da58-a1ef-f9dacca50000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔呼吁允许犹太人在圣殿山祈祷；内塔尼亚胡：现状“不会改变”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-calls-for-jews-to-pray-on-temple-mount-netanyahu-status-quo-will-not-change/0000018f-e9af-d463-a19f-fdbffea90000</link><description>这是以色列负责圣殿山/阿克萨清真寺安全的部长第一次公开背离该地点禁止犹太人在那里祈祷的现行现状。内塔尼亚胡总理很快反驳了极右翼部长的言论</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 19:45:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-calls-for-jews-to-pray-on-temple-mount-netanyahu-status-quo-will-not-change/0000018f-e9af-d463-a19f-fdbffea90000</guid></item><item><title>他们生活在一个遥远的星球上。但不幸的是，对于以色列来说，他们负责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-05/ty-article/.highlight/they-live-on-a-far-off-planet-but-unfortunately-for-israel-theyre-in-charge/0000018f-e971-da58-a1ef-f9f3967a0000</link><description>越来越多的情况是，总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的联盟成员似乎生活在某个遥远的星球上：在这个星球上，没有任何一个负责的成年人是错的，所说的事情使它们成为事实，而忽视问题则使问题消失</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 19:02:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-05/ty-article/.highlight/they-live-on-a-far-off-planet-but-unfortunately-for-israel-theyre-in-charge/0000018f-e971-da58-a1ef-f9f3967a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡和以色列将军秘密希望结束加沙战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-and-israels-generals-secretly-want-to-end-the-gaza-war/0000018f-e90c-d4cf-abcf-ef4d8e330000</link><description>首相总是希望有尽可能多的选择，他得出的结论是，他需要一个结束战争的选择。但他停止战斗的动机与他的将军们不同</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 17:34:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-and-israels-generals-secretly-want-to-end-the-gaza-war/0000018f-e90c-d4cf-abcf-ef4d8e330000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列校园里，犹太和巴勒斯坦学生创造了理智和希望的时刻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/on-an-israeli-campus-jewish-and-palestinian-students-carve-out-moments-of-sanity-and-hope/0000018f-e805-d0ea-a1bf-fb45d2c60000</link><description>在特拉维夫大学的 MiddleMeets 倡议中，阿拉伯和犹太学生互相谈论大屠杀、10 月 7 日大浩劫和加沙轰炸。目标：不放弃。它也能在美国校园的战场上发挥作用吗？</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 17:08:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/on-an-israeli-campus-jewish-and-palestinian-students-carve-out-moments-of-sanity-and-hope/0000018f-e805-d0ea-a1bf-fb45d2c60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 243 天：哈马斯与法塔赫之间的和解谈判定于 6 月中旬进行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-243-reconciliation-talks-between-hamas-fatah-set-for-june/0000018f-e957-dda1-a99f-ebd7182d0001</link><description>内塔尼亚胡表示，以色列“准备对真主党采取非常有力的行动” ■ 政府将投票授权以色列国防军在 8 月底前将现役预备役军人人数增加到 35 万人 ■ 武装人员向贝鲁特附近的美国大使馆开枪 ■ 哈马斯与以色列之间的和解谈判巴勒斯坦总统阿巴斯的法塔赫晚会将于 6 月中旬在中国举行 ■ 战争进入 243 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 17:05:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-243-reconciliation-talks-between-hamas-fatah-set-for-june/0000018f-e957-dda1-a99f-ebd7182d0001</guid></item></channel></rss>